### Basic usage

```jsx
<div
  style={{
    display: "flex",
    justifyContent: "space-evenly",
    alignItems: "center",
    width: "100%",
  }}
>
  <IconButton icon={Bolt} kind="primary" ariaLabel="My primary IconButton" />
  <IconButton
    icon={Bolt}
    kind="secondary"
    ariaLabel="My secondary IconButton"
  />
  <IconButton icon={Bolt} kind="tertiary" ariaLabel="My tertiary IconButton" />
</div>
```

